name: Vessels 178: The Devourer
description:
Life is full of opportunity and abundance and some people want more than their fair share.  

A life of greed, excess and dominance has brought the devourer to his position today.  Not well liked, but respected by the powerful for his ruthlessness he has risen high in society and acts as a bridge between the underworld and the elites.  

I am not saying he eats babies but I wouldn’t put it past him.  Those cold porcine eyes....
